A modern, responsive e-commerce website for snowboard equipment built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. Features a clean design, product filtering, shopping cart functionality, and mobile-responsive layout


Features
🛍️ E-commerce Functionality
Product Catalog: Display products fetched from API
Shopping Cart: Add, remove, and update product quantities
Local Storage: Cart persistence across browser sessions
Real-time Updates: Live cart count and total price calculation
🔍 Advanced Filtering & Search
Text Search: Search by product name, vendor, or tags
Price Range Filter: Filter products by price categories
Vendor Filter: Filter by product manufacturers
Sort Options: Sort by name (A-Z, Z-A) or price (Low-High, High-Low)
Clear Filters: Reset all filters with one click
📱 User Experience
Responsive Design: Mobile-first approach with Tailwind CSS
Loading States: Smooth loading animations and spinners
Error Handling: Graceful error messages and fallbacks
Notifications: Toast notifications for user actions
Smooth Scrolling: Seamless navigation between sections
🎨 Modern UI/UX
Card Hover Effects: Interactive product cards with animations
Sidebar Cart: Slide-out shopping cart with overlay
Mobile Menu: Collapsible navigation for mobile devices
Font Awesome Icons: Professional iconography throughout
🚀 Quick Start
Prerequisites
A modern web browser (Chrome, Firefox, Safari, Edge)
Basic understanding of HTML, CSS, and JavaScript (for customization)


snowboard/
├── index.html      # Main HTML file
├── styles.css      # Custom CSS styles
├── script.js       # JavaScript functionality
└── README.md       # This file


